	   <tr><td colspan=2>It's next to impossible to beat a Necro or a Mage of the same level ... if ever you do you've either gotten real lucky, or the opposition was stupid. Again, that's no slight to us Pallies, it's the way the game is slanted in favour of the Casters.<br>I started life on the PvPs and played a Monk. At level 5 I was forced to take on a Level 11 Mage and I nearly won. This was not because I was a great player, but was because the Mage sucked.<br>While at lower levels (ie. under 16) it should be easy for tanks to kill casters of similar level, at higher levels the disparities between tanks and casters becomes much more evident.<br>If you find yourself in a battle with a caster, your best bet is to fire off Flash of Light and Root and start Bashing and Slashing from behind them. Stun works great too (if you have it). Then, just hope for the best. Ignore the pets ... when you kill the caster the pet goes too.<br>&nbsp;<br>________<br><br>I've travelled this world and have seen many wondrous things. You are not one of them.</td></tr>
